## How to Run the Project

1. Install XAMPP
2. Start Apache and MySQL
3. Copy the project folder into the **htdocs** folder
4. Open phpMyAdmin
5. Import the database file (database.sql)
6. Open the browser and run:

http://localhost/criminal-database-system

